Comment: 0,0:00:15.26,0:00:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi.
Comment: 0,0:00:23.14,0:00:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:00:26.94,0:00:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi?
Comment: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:00:34.53,0:00:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Where are you, Kogarashi?
Comment: 0,0:00:40.66,0:00:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're being indecent in that state.
Comment: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When I woke up, Kogarashi was gone!
Comment: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D-Did he come to hate me after all\Nand decide to leave?
Comment: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi left this morning.
Comment: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After all, the high school\Nentrance ceremony is today.
Comment: 0,0:00:59.93,0:01:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}Yamaue Municipal\NYukemuri High School\NEntrance Ceremony
Comment: 0,0:01:05.73,0:01:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So this is my high school from today.
Comment: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When I think about it, it's been a hard road.
Comment: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}In elementary school,{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was often possessed by the spirits\Nof bronze statues and anatomical models.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}In middle school, I underwent\Nharsh training to be a spirit medium.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:01:22.29,0:01:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The dream of a normal school life\Nwas only a dream.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But now I can banish any and all evil spirits\Nwith just a punch!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The real springtime of my life starts today!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So this is the school\Nyou'll be going to, Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna? Why...
Comment: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ms. Nakai told me.
Comment: 0,0:01:47.06,0:01:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wanted to celebrate your starting school.
Comment: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh yeah.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Normal humans can't see Yuuna.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:33.04,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna Goes to School
Comment: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi. I'm Satoshi Hyodo. What's your name?
Comment: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm Kogarashi Fuyuzora. Good to meet you.
Comment: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We're pretty lucky.
Comment: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chisaki Miyazaki is in this class.
Comment: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Miyazaki?
Comment: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, you seriously don't know about her?
Comment: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Look, she's over there. The totally cute girl!
Comment: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rumor has it she's always being scouted out\Nto be a model, but refuses every time.
Comment: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That mild-mannered part of her\Nis also really great.
Comment: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, really? I'm looking forward to it.
Comment: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, Yuuna, what are you...
Comment: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wonder what this is made of.
Comment: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're the worst.
Comment: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- I didn't...\N- Hey, that guy lifted Chisaki's skirt!
Comment: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- You're kidding me!\N- Who is that guy?
Comment: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you, Fuyuzora?\NYou're terrible.
Comment: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It wasn't me!
Comment: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I just got so focused.
Comment: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sheesh, what are you doing?
Comment: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I thought I'd change into a school uniform, too.
Comment: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Change?
Comment: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This yukata is actually part of my spiritual body.
Comment: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can change clothes\Nby focusing on an image in my head.
Comment: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, here I go.
Comment: 0,0:04:54.83,0:05:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If your clothes are part of your spiritual body,\Nthen it's like you're always naked?
Comment: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm always naked?
Comment: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna?
Comment: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Calm down! Nobody else can see you!
Comment: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora, who are you talking to?
Comment: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No!
Comment: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- We're floating!\N- What?
Comment: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna!
Comment: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What the...
Comment: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A magic trick?
Comment: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's with the ruckus in here?
Comment: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're slacking off on the first day of school!
Comment: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I know you're excited, but remember\Nyou're high school students now
Comment: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,so you should lead your school life properly.
Comment: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right, I'll have you\Nintroduce yourselves in order.
Comment: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}We'll start with Aikawa.
Comment: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We got lectured on the first day of school?
Comment: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Here. I'm Ryoko Aikawa.
Comment: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Whoever did that trick is a real jerk.
Comment: 0,0:05:56.14,0:06:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I went to Yukemuri Middle School before this\Nand was on the basketball team.
Comment: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We also got a guy in here\Nwho lifted up Miyazaki's skirt.
Comment: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}There are several other former classmates from\Nmiddle school, but I hope to make new friends.
Comment: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The true springtime of my life...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still, I have to take responsibility.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}- Next. Fuyuzora.\N- Here.
Comment: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm Fuyuzora Kogarashi.
Comment: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I just moved here, so I would love it\Nif you told me about your town.
Comment: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Also...
Comment: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm a spirit medium.
Comment: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A spirit medium?
Comment: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Before, everything was floating in the room
Comment: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,because of me and the poltergeist activity\Ngenerated by a ghost I brought with me.
Comment: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi.
Comment: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I apologize for causing a scene.
Comment: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, too!
Comment: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Spirits and poltergeist?
Comment: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}First he lifts up a skirt,\Nand now he's delusional?
Comment: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}We've got a cringey one here!
Comment: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, this is expected.
Comment: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, everyone! He's not lying.
Comment: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But they can't hear my voice, can they?
Comment: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I just wanted to apologize.
Comment: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If anybody has any problems with evil spirits\Nor monsters, you can come to me for advice.
Comment: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,See you, Fuyuzora!
Comment: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Watch out for ghosts on the way home!
Comment: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't lift any more skirts!
Comment: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I won't!
Comment: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry. This was my fault.
Comment: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I said it's all right.
Comment: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I never intended to hide\Nmy psychic power anyway.
Comment: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Fuyuzora.
Comment: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Miyazaki?
Comment: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uh, Miyazaki? If this is about your skirt,\NI'm sorry. I really am.
Comment: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's right.\NThat really was an awful thing to do.
Comment: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But that's not why I want to talk to you.
Comment: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this mood?
Comment: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm here, too, you know!
Comment: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I think you're the only one.
Comment: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No!
Comment: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's what happened.\NThat's supernatural phenomenon, right?
Comment: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, that's why she wanted to talk to him.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But then, I also saw...
Comment: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In the middle of the night,\Nmy stuffed animals were flying around.
Comment: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I got really scared.
Comment: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry. If I suddenly tell you this,\NI'm just being a nuisance, huh?
Comment: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you'd like, I'd be happy to help you.
Comment: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't just do nothing\Nwhen my classmate is troubled.
Comment: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you, Fuyuzora!
Comment: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's amazing, Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right, first,\Nwhy don't we go to your place, Miyazaki?
Comment: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Would there be a problem?
Comment: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But, Fuyuzora...
Comment: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,you're a pervert.
Comment: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do?\NI only intended to ask him for advice.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So this is the room\Nwhere the stuffed animals were flying?
Comment: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There are so many stuffed animals in here!
Comment: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wh-What should I do?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the first time\NI let a boy into my bedroom!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fuyuzora isn't a bad guy, is he?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems like he didn't lift my skirt up\Non purpose either.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If Fuyuzora gets in the mood, as a girl, I can't...
Comment: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, Miyazaki.
Comment: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Comment: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,These are the ones\Nthat are giving you problems, right?
Comment: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All I could think of was that\Nsomething was possessing them.
Comment: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want you to help them.
Comment: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right. First I'll try to exorcise them.
Comment: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exorcise? Like a real spirit medium!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No!
Comment: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Comment: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You have a nice punch there, Miyazaki.
Comment: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That was mean. Beating up on the stuffed animals\Nshe cares so much about.
Comment: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I said I was exorcising them.
Comment: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That was an exorcism?
Comment: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If spirits were inside them,\Nthey would've been beaten out by now.
Comment: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But I didn't see anything come out.
Comment: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's with this guy? He's too violent!\NIs he really a spirit medium?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This means the culprit\Nmust be controlling them from somewhere.
Comment: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Controlling?
Comment: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,According to my mentor, it's done\Nwith a special seal that's been implanted.
Comment: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So Yuuna...
Comment: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes?
Comment: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Can you check the inside of this guy?
Comment: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You can go through it,\Nso you can see inside, right?
Comment: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Comment: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, I've been wondering,\Nwho's this Yuuna?
Comment: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You can't see her, huh?
Comment: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I mentioned her at school, remember?\NShe's not a bad person, so don't worry.
Comment: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:56.46,0:12:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's my fault Kogarashi's reputation\Nhas suffered at school,{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}so I have to be useful at least a little.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry, Miyazaki!
Comment: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please leave!
Comment: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He was just some perverted guy!
Comment: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I bet you being a spirit medium was a lie!
Comment: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is a misunderstanding! Please listen!
Comment: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh boy.
Comment: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I guess we just wait and see now.
Comment: 0,0:12:57.98,0:12:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I was too harsh on Fuyuzora.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But anyone would have done the same thing.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if these guys\Nwill move by themselves again.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What? Hey!
Comment: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't! Stop it, everyone!
Comment: 0,0:13:47.87,0:13:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?
Comment: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Somebody!
Comment: 0,0:13:58.92,0:13:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Comment: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora?
Comment: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fighting them won't solve anything.
Comment: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Comment: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go where?
Comment: 0,0:14:08.35,0:14:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's obvious. To punch out the culprit!
Comment: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll make myself useful!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to follow the plan!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}What should we do now?
Comment: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Do you know what a spirit line is?
Comment: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Spirit line?
Comment: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's like an electric line that someone\Nwith spells can run spirit energy through.
Comment: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When that monk attacked you that one time,\Nhe wrapped you in streams of light, remember?
Comment: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right. So that's what it is?
Comment: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Spirit lines can only be seen when someone\Nsends spirit energy flowing through them.
Comment: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So we pretended to leave Miyazaki's house\Nand wait for the culprit to use their spells again.
Comment: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see!
Comment: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When we see the spirit line stretching out\Nfrom Miyazaki's room, you follow it from the air,
Comment: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and find the culprit on the other end.
Comment: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay, Kogarashi!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- We're going, too!\N- Wait! I'm not dressed...
Comment: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi! Over here!
Comment: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's you, huh?
Comment: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why are you animating stuffed animals?
Comment: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't get cocky just because\Nyou can use some psychic power.
Comment: 0,0:15:27.42,0:15:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That isn't the only spell I have.
Comment: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's that?
Comment: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A leaf turned into a monster?
Comment: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora.
Comment: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Do it.
Comment: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please run, Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Comment: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now would you care to explain?
Comment: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Otherwise...
Comment: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You understand, don't you?
Comment: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Comment: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A girl?
Comment: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll apologize, so please forgive me!
Comment: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm Koyuzu Shigaraki.
Comment: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I came from a village of supernatural raccoons.
Comment: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In my clan, when we become ten years old,
Comment: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,we learn sorcery that involves leaves,\Nand then depart the village to live on our own.
Comment: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All by yourself?
Comment: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm actually supposed to transform\Ninto an adult and blend into society,
Comment: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but I'm bad at transforming.
Comment: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You do look like an elementary school student.
Comment: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't have a place to live, so I've been\Nstaying at an abandoned temple all alone.
Comment: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But I know this isn't how\Na member of a raccoon clan should be.
Comment: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But that's when I saw you, Chisaki.
Comment: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So I put my leaves\Nin your stuffed animals and observed you.
Comment: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After all, you have\Nthe one thing that I lack the most!
Comment: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What you lack?
Comment: 0,0:17:58.28,0:17:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I...
Comment: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...lack boobs!
Comment: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Boobs?
Comment: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I think boobs are important for an adult female!
Comment: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If I only had boobs, then I could...
Comment: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Comment: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When a spirit medium showed up,\NI figured it was all over.
Comment: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So I just wanted to see\NChisaki's boobs one last time.
Comment: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's why you were so forceful.
Comment: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I did something bad.
Comment: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Comment: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now that I know what it's about,\Nand if my chest is okay, then...
Comment: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Really?
Comment: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you, Chisaki!
Comment: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chisaki's boobs are so beautiful!
Comment: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No!
Comment: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora, you saw, didn't you?
Comment: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,N-No, I didn't.
Comment: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You saw! I'm sure you did!
Comment: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You really do have a dirty mind!
Comment: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}And so the curtain goes down\Non the Chisaki Miyazaki affair.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}It was decided that Koyuzu Shigaraki\Nwould stay at Yuragi Inn for the time being.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's another nice day, huh?
Comment: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You did good work yesterday.
Comment: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,\Nyou're a bound spirit, right, Yuuna?
Comment: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And yet you can fly around so freely.
Comment: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,True, a long time ago, I couldn't\Ngo outside the boundaries of Yuragi Inn.
Comment: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But after some trial and error, I'm now\Nonly bound to the inn when I go to sleep.
Comment: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've been a ghost for a long time, remember?
Comment: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ghosts have it rough too, huh?
Comment: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, Fuyuzora!
Comment: 0,0:19:57.99,0:19:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Comment: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Miyazaki.
Comment: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, thank you for yesterday.
Comment: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, what happened with Koyuzu afterwards?
Comment: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, regarding her...
Comment: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Comment: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You mustn't, Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hold still. We'll get you all clean.
Comment: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sweet boobs!
Comment: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, you're making it hard for me to wash you.
Comment: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She seemed pretty excited.
Comment: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see. Good to hear.
Comment: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tell her I'll stop by for a visit next time.
Comment: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sure.
Comment: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, Fuyuzora.
Comment: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know if this is a proper gift, but...
Comment: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I baked some cookies.\NPlease have them if you'd like.
Comment: 0,0:20:52.29,0:20:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cookies, you say?
Comment: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been living in debtor hell for years!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter how much I saved up, I thought\NI could never afford a snack in my lifetime!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- That's the best gift ever, Miyazaki!\N- Really?
Comment: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tell Yuuna I said hi, too.
Comment: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I have class clean-up duty today,\Nso I'll go on ahead.
Comment: 0,0:21:18.78,0:21:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay. See you later.
Comment: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going back home.
Comment: 0,0:21:24.53,0:21:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If I go to school with you again,\NI'll just cause more trouble.
Comment: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If it's about yesterday, don't worry about it.
Comment: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But...
Comment: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It was troubling at the time,\Nbut because you caused that ruckus,
Comment: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I made friends with Miyazaki\Nand Koyuzu in the end.
Comment: 0,0:21:43.43,0:21:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And I also get to have a snack\Nfor the first time in a while.
Comment: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Doesn't sound bad to me.
Comment: 0,0:21:48.68,0:21:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right.
Comment: 0,0:21:51.18,0:21:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,These cookies are really good!
Comment: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Have one, Yuuna!
Comment: 0,0:21:55.15,0:21:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you give it to me as an offering,\NI'll be able to taste it.
Comment: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It is delicious!
Comment: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Comment: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Next time: Watching Youkai!\NSagiri and Yaya are Cautious.
Comment: 0,0:23:36.79,0:23:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't miss...
Comment: 0,0:23:37.87,0:23:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.94,0:00:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.53,0:00:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kogarashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cậu đâu rồi, Kogarashi-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.66,0:00:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ăn mặc như thế là không được đâu đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Khi em dậy thì Kogarashi-san đã biến đâu mất tiêu rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,K-Không lẽ cậu ấy không thích em rồi đi khỏi đây rồi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-kun đi từ sáng rồi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bởi hôm nay là ngày lễ nhập học ở trường cấp 3 mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.73,0:01:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Từ hôm nay mình sẽ học ở trường cấp 3 này!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nghĩ lại thấy trước giờ mình đã trải qua lắm chông gai thử thách.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:14.24,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Hồi tiểu học...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:18.37,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,thì hay bị vong của pho tượng đồng với bộ mô hình cơ thể người ám.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:22.29,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Đến khi lên cấp 2 thì phải tu luyện rất khắc nghiệt để trở thành linh lực giả.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.29,0:01:25.96,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Giấc mộng có được đời học sinh bình thường mãi chỉ là giấc mộng.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:31.46,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng giờ thì mình có thể đấm bay bất kỳ con yêu ma nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:34.88,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Hôm nay là ngày thanh xuân của mình thực sự bắt đầu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ra đây là trường mà Kogarashi-san sắp theo học.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna? Sao cậu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nakai-san nói cho mình biết đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.06,0:01:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình chỉ muốn chúc mừng cậu đi học thôi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:52.90,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,À ra vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:56.57,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Người thường không thấy được Yuuna mà nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:33.04,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna đến trường
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chào, tớ là Hyodo Satoshi, còn cậu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora Kogarashi, hân hạnh được gặp cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tụi mình hên lắm luôn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Miyazaki Chisaki cũng học lớp này đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Miyazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Này này, đừng nói là cậu không biết nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhỏ ấy đứng kia kìa, dễ thương lắm phải không nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Có tin đồn rằng lắm lần nhỏ ấy được mời về làm người mẫu, nhưng nhỏ đều từ chối hết.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Phần con người hoà nhã trong nhỏ ấy cũng tuyệt lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thật vậy à? Mình háo hức muốn xem quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Này, Yuuna, làm cái gì thế hả...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không biết cái này được làm từ gì nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rác rưởi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Không phải...!\N- Này, thằng đó dám lật váy của Chisaki-chan kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Không đùa đấy chứ?!\N- Thằng đó là ai vậy chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tự nhiên làm cái gì vậy hả Fuyuzora?! Quá đáng thật đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không phải!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi cậu, do mình chú tâm quá nên...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thiệt là, làm cái gì thế hả...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình nghĩ có thể thay thành đồng phục học sinh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thật ra bộ yukata này là một phần linh thể của mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nếu tập trung suy nghĩ một bộ khác trong đầu thì có thể thay thành bộ đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy, mình thay đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:05:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nếu quần áo là một phần linh thể của cậu, thì chẳng phải lúc nào cậu cũng khoả thân à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lúc nào mình cũng khoả thân á?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bình tĩnh đi, không có ai thấy cậu đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora, đang nói chuyện với ai thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Mình đang lơ lửng này!\N- Cái gì?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chuyện gì thế...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ảo thuật à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gì mà ồn như cái chợ vậy hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mới ngày đầu đi học đã làm loạn lên rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thầy biết các em rất hào hứng, nhưng hãy nhớ giờ bản thân đã là học sinh cấp 3 rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,nên phải để đời học sinh thật đàng hoàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Được rồi, giờ thì từng em tự giới thiệu nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mới ngày đầu đi học đã bị ăn mắng ư?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không biết kẻ nào đã bày ra cái trò ảo thuật đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Còn tên kia thì dám lật váy Miyazaki nữa chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:04.94,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Ôi thanh xuân thực sự của mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình xin lỗi, Kogarashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:12.12,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng mà, mình phải chịu trách nhiệm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Tiếp theo, Fuyuzora.\N- Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em là Fuyuzora Kogarashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tớ vừa mới chuyển tới đây, nên nếu được mọi người chỉ bảo, thì tớ sẽ rất vui.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Và còn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tớ là một linh lực giả.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Linh lực giả?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lúc này, mọi thứ trong phòng lơ lửng trên không trung...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,là do tớ và poltergeist của một hồn ma tớ đưa theo gây ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi vì đã gây rắc rối cho các bạn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình cũng xin lỗi mọi người!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Linh lực giả?! Poltergeist?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nãy thì lật váy, giờ thì bị ảo tưởng à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lớp mình có một tên dở hơi rồi đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Biết ngay sẽ thế này mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mọi người, cậu ấy không đùa đâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cơ mà họ lại không nghe thấy mình nói gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tớ chỉ muốn xin lỗi mọi người thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nếu có ai gặp vấn đề về ma quỷ thì có thể trao đổi với tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy nhé, Fuyuzora!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhớ cẩn thận kẻo bị ma bắt mất đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đừng có lật váy người ta nữa nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không có mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thực sự xin lỗi cậu, là lỗi của mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đã nói là không sao mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tớ cũng đâu có định giấu linh lực của bản thân.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À, Fuyuzora-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Miyazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À, Miyazaki, nếu là chuyện cái váy thì cho tớ xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Phải rồi nhỉ, làm thế là quá đáng lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng đó không phải chuyện tớ muốn nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B-Bầu không khí này là...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Có mình ở đây nữa nè...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tớ nghĩ chỉ có cậu mới được thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:49.44,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chuyện là vậy đấy, đó là hiện tượng siêu nhiên phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đúng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:59.95,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Tưởng gì, ra là muốn nói chuyện đó à.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sau đó tớ còn thấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đến giữa đêm, mấy con thú nhồi bông lại bay lơ lửng quanh phòng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tớ sợ lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi cậu, tự nhiên nói ra chuyện này, hẳn phiền cho cậu lắm nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nếu không phiền, thì tớ sẽ giúp cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bạn cùng lớp gặp chuyện thì sao có thể làm ngơ được.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cảm ơn cậu, Fuyuzora-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san mà lị.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy, tới nhà Miyazaki xem thử nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Có vấn đề gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thì bởi, Fuyuzora-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,biến thái lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:51.88,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Tính sao giờ?! Mình chỉ muốn xin cậu ấy lời khuyên thôi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đây là phòng có mấy con thú nhồi bông biết bay à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhiều thú nhồi bông ghê!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:01.51,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,T-Tính sao giờ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:05.89,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Đây là lần đầu mình để con trai vào phòng riêng mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:09.15,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora-kun không phải người xấu đâu nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:12.86,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Có lẽ cậu ấy không cố ý lật váy mình đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.49,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:22.33,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Lỡ như Fuyuzora-kun mà hứng lên, thì phận con gái như mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Này, Miyazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C-Chuyện gì?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chuyện xảy ra với mấy con này phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình nghĩ là có gì đó đã ám chúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nên mới nhờ cậu giúp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Được rồi, thử trừ tà trước xem nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:44.56,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Trừ tà?! Linh lực giả thứ thiệt rồi đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cậu làm cái gì vậy hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cú đấm có lực lắm đấy, Miyazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế là quá đáng lắm đó, cậu ấy quý mấy con thú nhồi bông đó vậy mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thì tớ chỉ trừ tà thôi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vừa rồi đó à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nếu có vong bên trong, thì bọn chúng sẽ bị đánh bay ra ngay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng xem ra chẳng có gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:22.26,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Cậu ta bị cái thứ gì thế không biết?!\NBạo lực như thế có thật là linh lực giả không thế?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế tức là thủ phạm điều khiển chúng từ một nơi khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Điều khiển?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Theo lời sư phụ tớ, thì hắn ta điều khiển bằng cách đưa một phong ấn đặc biệt vào trong chúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy, Yuuna...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vâng?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cậu kiểm tra bên trong con này được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cậu có thể đi xuyên qua nó, nên xem bên trong được mà phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À, vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nè, nãy giờ tớ cứ thắc mắc, Yuuna là ai thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Miyazaki không thấy được mà ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lúc nãy tớ nói ở trường rồi mà, nhỏ ấy không phải người xấu đâu, nên đừng lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:56.46,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Được rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:12:00.43,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Do mình mà Kogarashi-san mới bị tiếng xấu ở trường.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:02.30,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,nên chí ít mình phải giúp cậu ấy được gì đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi, Miyazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Về đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Quả nhiên cậu ta chỉ là tên biến thái thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chuyện linh lực giả chỉ là xạo thôi chứ gì!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cậu hiểu lầm rồi!? Nghe mình giải thích cái đã.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thôi bể chuyện rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thôi thì ngồi đợi quan sát tình hình vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:12:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:21.09,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Có lẽ mình hơi quá lời với Fuyuzora-kun rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.88,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng làm gì có ai phạm phải cùng một sai lầm tới 2 lần.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:28.85,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Không biết mấy đứa có tự động di chuyển nữa không...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gì thế?! Khoan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không! Dừng lại đi mà, mấy đứa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.87,0:13:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sao mấy đứa lại...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Có ai không?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:13:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cậu không sao chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đánh nhau với chúng không giải quyết được vấn đề đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đi nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đi đâu cơ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.35,0:14:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Còn phải nói sao, đi đá đi thủ phạm chứ đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:21.44,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình phải tỏ ra có ích mới được!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:22.94,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Phải theo chiến lược đã đề ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:25.95,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy giờ phải làm sao đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:27.95,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Cậu biết linh tử tuyến chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:29.03,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Linh tử tuyến?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:33.24,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Nó giống như dòng điện được tạo ra nhờ thi triển thuật chú vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:38.46,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Hồi trước, khi cậu bị tên hoà thượng tấn công, hắn đã trói cậu bằng 1 sợi dây ánh sáng, nhớ không?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:41.17,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Vâng, ra là cái đó à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:47.05,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Ta chỉ thấy được linh tử tuyến khi có người đưa linh lực vào dòng chảy của chúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:51.55,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế nên chúng ta sẽ vờ như đã rời khỏi nhà Miyazaki, rồi đợi tới khi thủ phạm sử dụng thuật chú.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:53.39,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Ra là vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:58.48,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Khi thấy linh tử tuyến phóng ra từ phòng của Miyazaki, cậu sẽ bám theo nó...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:00.06,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,để tóm thủ phạm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:02.32,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Vâng, Kogarashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Bọn mình cũng đi thôi!\N- Khoan, tớ còn chưa mặc đồ...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san! Đằng kia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ra là ngươi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sao ngươi lại khiến mấy con thú nhồi bông di chuyển hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đừng có nghĩ mình là linh lực giả thì có thể lên giọng với ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.42,0:15:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thuật chú của ta không chỉ có nhiêu đó đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gì thế này?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chiếc lá hoá thành con quái vật ư?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xử chúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mau chạy đi, Kogarashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tuyệt thật...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Giờ thì giải thích cho bọn này nghe được chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hay là muốn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ngươi hiểu mà phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,X-Xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Con gái?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em xin lỗi rồi mà, tha cho em đi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em là Shigaraki Koyuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em đến từ làng chồn tinh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trong gia tộc của em, khi lên 10 tuổi,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,thì phải học được diệp thuật, rồi rời làng sống một mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Một mình?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thực ra là phải biến thân thành người lớn để hoà nhập vào xã hội loài người,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,nhưng em lại không giỏi phép biến hình.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhìn kiểu gì cũng giống học sinh tiểu học nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em không có nơi nào để sống, nên trước giờ chỉ biết chui lủi một mình trong một ngôi đền bỏ hoang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dù biết người của tộc chồn tinh thì không được như thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế rồi em đã gặp được Chisaki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế là em đã đặt mấy cái lá vào lũ thú nhồi bông để nghiên cứu chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bởi vì, chị có một thứ mà em không hề có!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không hề có?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:17:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,hổng có vếu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vếu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em nghĩ vếu rất quan trọng với cánh chị em trưởng thành.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nếu có vếu thì em có thể...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thật thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Khi linh lực giả xuất hiện thì em đã biết mọi chuyện đã an bài.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nên là em chỉ muốn ngắm vếu Chisaki-chan 1 lần cuối này nữa thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế nên em mới cố đến vậy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em xin lỗi vì đã làm những chuyện quá đáng với chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không sao đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Giờ chị đã rõ sự tình rồi, nếu là ngực của chị thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thật không ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cảm ơn chị, Chisaki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Quả nhiên vếu của Chisaki-chan quá đẹp luôn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora-kun, cậu thấy rồi phải không?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C-Chưa thấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhất định là thấy rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Quả nhiên cậu chỉ là tên biến thái thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:16.86,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Và, vụ án của Miyazaki Chisaki khép lại ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:25.20,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy là Shigaraki Koyuzu sẽ phải tới làm phiền những người ở nhà trọ Yuragi một thời gian rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hôm nay trời đẹp ghê ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hôm qua cậu đã vất vả rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nói mới nhớ, Yuuna là hồn ma bị chôn chân mà nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy mà cậu có thể bay nhảy tự do thế này.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đúng là hồi xưa mình không thể ra ngoài khuôn viên nhà trọ Yuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng sau khi thử nhiều cách, thì giờ tớ chỉ bị chôn chân ở nhà trọ khi đi ngủ thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hồn ma lão làng mà lị.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Làm ma cũng lắm phiền phức nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:19:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chào buổi sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Miyazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À, chuyện hôm qua cảm ơn cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Koyuzu-chan từ hôm qua tới giờ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À, nếu là con bé thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Quá ghê!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế là hổng được đâu, Kogarashi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ngồi yên để chị kì cơ thể cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vếu quá đẹp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Này, đừng có làm khó chị vậy chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hình như con bé khoái lắm đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ra vậy, thế thì tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bảo với con bé lần sau ghé qua nhà tớ chơi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À, Fuyuzora-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không biết cậu có thích món quà này không...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tớ có làm ít bánh quy, nếu muốn thì cậu có thể mang về ăn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.29,0:20:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bánh quy ư?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:59.17,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Mấy năm qua đã phải sống trong cảnh nợ nần...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:04.76,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Tiết kiệm như trâu như bò mà tới bây giờ đến gói snack mình cũng chả mua nổi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Cậu là nhất đó, Miyazaki!\N- Thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cho tớ gửi lời chào đến Yuuna-san nữa nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hôm nay tớ còn phải trực lớp, nên tớ đi trước nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.78,0:21:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ừ, gặp cậu sau.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy, mình về đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.53,0:21:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nếu mình theo cậu tới trường thì sẽ gây ra rắc rối nữa mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nếu là chuyện hôm qua thì đừng để bụng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đúng là lúc đó cậu đã gây ra chuyện, nhưng cũng nhờ cậu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,mà tớ có thể kết thân với Miyazaki và Koyuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.43,0:21:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Và cũng nhờ đó mà tớ mới được ăn bánh quy trong suốt mấy năm qua.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế thì tốt chứ sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.68,0:21:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.18,0:21:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bánh quy ngon ghê!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna ăn thử đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.15,0:21:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À, nếu có người cúng thì mình mới nếm thử được.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ngon quá đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thấy chưa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:40.00,Next Title,NTP,0,0,0,,THEO DÕI YÊU QUÁI! SAGIRI-SAN\NYAYA, RỤT RÈ RỤT RÈ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.79,0:23:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tập tiếp theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.87,0:23:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đừng bỏ lỡ nhé.
